"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Children &gt;12 years and Adults: 40-250 mg after meals and at bedtime as needed, not to exceed 500 mg/day",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
